WEBVTT


00:00:00.040 --> 00:00:01.900
Is Shirakawa worth visiting?

00:00:01.960 --> 00:00:03.320
Shirakawa was designated

00:00:03.320 --> 00:00:05.760
as UNESCO World Heritage in 1995.

00:00:05.760 --> 00:00:08.000
It is a secluded region surrounded by nature,

00:00:08.000 --> 00:00:10.080
famous for its gosho zukudi villages.

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:12.000
The Waterhouse is one of the largest gosho

00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:13.160
style houses in the area

00:00:13.160 --> 00:00:15.200
and the only one designated as a National

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:16.660
Important Cultural Property.

00:00:16.680 --> 00:00:18.240
You can also dine in Kitano Shore

00:00:18.240 --> 00:00:19.880
at 250 year old building

00:00:19.880 --> 00:00:22.920
and enjoy the miso steak set meal with grilled Rockfish.

00:00:22.920 --> 00:00:24.320
Wanna visit Shirakagogo?

00:00:24.320 --> 00:00:25.310
Let me know in the comment section.
